  "title": "Van Driver #79611",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Food & Beverage</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Van Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ubi</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Mon – Sat, 10.00am – 7.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $3,000 + OT + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive and operate company vehicle to deliver food items to various event locations</li><li>Conduct regular inspections and basic maintenance on the vehicle</li><li>Assist with the loading and unloading of goods</li><li>Maintain accurate records of deliveries</li><li>Adhere to all road safety regulations and company safety policies</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O-level/NITEC required</li><li>Must have a valid Class 3 driving license</li><li>Prior driving experience in catering industry is an added advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79611 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
